description: Essential for any true American pastime, the Football causes confusion to attacks due to the concussive reputation of the sport it represents.
name: Football

description: The Baseball Bat is an object of pride around Lakewood High School, a dangerous weapon that anyone can use to put their fellow classmates to sleep. Enjoy!
name: Baseball Bat

description: A sport unknown to the halls of Lakewood, lacrosse equipment is a rare occurrence. The Lacrosse Stick launches hard rubber balls at the enemy, to a varying degree of success.
name: Lacrosse Stick

description: Terrorizing fourth grade gym classes for centuries, the Dodgeball flies toward its victims like a fireball, adding Fire damage to prospective attacks.
name: Dodgeball

description: No cheerleader is complete without a signature accessory, Glitter. Glitter flies in bursts towards enemies and gets places Glitter should never go.
name: Glitter

description: This bow is typically used to hold hair up and look pretty, but when needed the bow can shoot magical projectiles toward foes.
name: Bow

description: What better way to express excitement to the audience than with Outdoor Voice, a sonic boom of pep which invigorates an audience and destroys enemies.
name: Outdoor Voice

description: The ultimate weapon in school spirit, what is a cheerleader without her/his Pom Poms. Pom Poms blast the enemy with a tremendous amount of power, sending them into a tailspin of pain.
name: Pom-Poms

description: Straight from your local Hot Topic is the greatest album of 2004. Make enemies feel the emoness of you Frerard Fanfiction with the MCR CD.
name: MCR CD

description: Who ever said that eyeliner wasn’t supposed to cover the entire face? With the Eyeliner Dagger foes will really feel how sharp wings can really be.
name: Eyeliner Dagger

description: Warp Tour is right around the corner, know what that means? Rave Glow-Sticks! Distract enemies with the glowing lights and pretty colors.
name: Rave Glow-Sticks

description: Full of a certain someone’s most intimate secrets and memories, Raven’s Diary is full of angst and sadness from the Emo herself. Raven’s Diary makes targets cower in fear at the sound of her thoughts.
name: Raven's Diary

description: No band is complete without the tones provided by the saxophone, this golden instrument captivates audiences with the power of the wind, the woodwind.
name: Saxophone

description: The Keyboard is a piece of hardware from the olden days of computing, with obnoxiously clicky keys and a barf yellow aesthetic. Being wacked by this weapon causes head trauma, as well as a chance to cause a knockout.
name: Keyboard

description: No Frodo cosplay is complete without Sting, the slayer of spiders. Sting glows when in the presence of goblins and orcs but there are none of those in this game. Have fun!
name: Sting (Spider's Bane)

description: Rolling the D20 is of sacred importance in D7D. Traditionally the 20 sided dice is used for stat allocation, but this D20 restores health with every attack.
name: D20

description: Enemies know this isn't just any bow. The Crossbow has LED reticles, glow-in-the-dark arrows, and a fancy wrsitband.
name: Crossbow

description: Dueling with Banjos has never been easier with the Fiddle. The Fiddle fascinates the enemy with its carefree tones as well as keep the Devil down in Georgia where he belongs.
name: Fiddle

description: What is a man without his tractor? This green and yellow behemoth overcomes the enemy and has a large chance to incapacitate
name: John Deere Tractor

description: Genuine Copenhagen, the best and most disgusting of dip. Spitting this in the direction of enemies results in Rage and Confusion as to why someone would utilize Satan's Bubblegum.
name: Dip Can

description: Overcome the enemy with the heat of the Flamin' Hot Cheetos. With a chance to enrage the enemy, how many can you take?
name: Flamin' Hot Cheetos

description: An Herbalists work results in eyes bloodhsot with frustration, and Eye Drops prevent enemies from seeing this imperfection. Multiple uses ensure that eyes are as clear as water.
name: Eye Drops

description: These scales are used to measure things that make a person as blind as Justice. Use the Scales of Justice to determine the fate of the enemy with a chance for tremendous damage.
name: Scales of Justice

description: Kick back, relax, and enjoy the classic that is Good Burger. With new and improved visuals, Good Burger Blu-Ray regenerates health as well as do substancial damage to foes.
name: Good Burger Blu-Ray

description: Many a 12-year-old has spent hours exploring caverns for diamonds and other resources, only to be foiled by lava and Creepers. The Diamond Pickaxe is the fruits of all that exstensive labor.
name: Diamond Pickaxe

description: Study jutsus with the Ninja Hand-Sign Manual and show enemiest he power that comes along with skills such as Lotus Flower attacks. Remember, practice makes perfect.
name: Ninja Hand-Sign Manual

description: We do not speak his name, but his slimey green skin haunts the darkest corners of the internet. His image has been perverted and he is out for revenge.
name: The Forbidden Meme

description: You know Asuna from SAO? Yah we wish we could forget too. But her body pillow sure is comfortable as a senpai and cuddle buddy.
name: Asuna from SAO Body Pillow

description: The buttons of this guitar are covered in the Dorito dusted fingerprints of a true Guitar Hero, pacemaker42. Feel the power of this legendary weapon that has aided gamers through fire and flames.
name: Guitar Hero Controller

description: Basic Placeholder
name: Basic Sward
